title: Osthi Maamey Lyrics Osthi Song Lyrics
stanzas:
Singers : Baba Sehgal.Ranjith,Rahul Nambiar,Naveen
Song: Osthe Maamey
Lyrics : Vaali

Tamil Naatu cop-u dhaan
darani ellaam top dhaan.. osthi
Thupaakiyil thotaadhaan
naa eduthu pottaa dhaan.. osthi
Andha bollywood, indha kollywood
kaana robinhood,naandhaanada maamey

Edupen robber kitta, kodupen labour kitta
edhukum thuninja katta naandhaana da
osthi maamey,osthi maamey
osthi maamey,osthi maamey
osthi maamey, osthi maamey (Tamil Naatu ...)

Paathadhunda Jackyjaanin police story
paathirundha sollum adhu namma seidhi
kolla panam alli varraan mollamaari
kondu vandhu serkaporaan koopam-Cheri
Yaarum thapputhanda panna kannda opaathavan
odambu appuraama uppukannadhaan
aelumbu kannaa-pinna kandam thundan-dhaan

Naan dhaan inspecter-u, theriyum encounter-u
edhilum all-rounder-u, ennaalumdhaan maamey
Eduppen revolver-u, pidipen dunbaakuru
aruppen danguvaaru,adra naandhan

Ada annaatha aaduraaru, othiko othiko
ada sakka podu poduvaaru, othuko othuko

Terror-inu vandhu ninna terror ivan
thozhar-inu vandhu ninna thozhar ivan
Unnapozha unna kaatum mirror ivan
Enna pola innoruthan inga evan

Aaana kallaerinja kannaadidhaan

iruku enndudaya macham macham dhaan

udhadu theepidikum koopunudhaan maamey
